{"tid":1150472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜魯多致電特朗普　華府支持促中國釋放加國公民","createTime":"2019-05-12T00:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T02:34:12.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5569cda55aeb79dcf40cccbe774d9afea3128c","tid":1150472,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T00:31:25.000Z","msg":"杜魯多致電特朗普　華府支持促中國釋放加國公民 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190510/s00004/1557456795000/%e6%9d%9c%e9%ad%af%e5%a4%9a%e8%87%b4%e9%9b%bb%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae-%e8%8f%af%e5%ba%9c%e6%94%af%e6%8c%81%e4%bf%83%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e9%87%8b%e6%94%be%e5%8a%a0%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%ac%e6%b0%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190510%2Fs00004%2F1557456795000%2F%25e6%259d%259c%25e9%25ad%25af%25e5%25a4%259a%25e8%2587%25b4%25e9%259b%25bb%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae-%25e8%258f%25af%25e5%25ba%259c%25e6%2594%25af%25e6%258c%2581%25e4%25bf%2583%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%2587%258b%25e6%2594%25be%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2585%25ac%25e6%25b0%2591&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNWyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=b564ef84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190510%2Fs00004%2F1557456795000%2F%25e6%259d%259c%25e9%25ad%25af%25e5%25a4%259a%25e8%2587%25b4%25e9%259b%25bb%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae-%25e8%258f%25af%25e5%25ba%259c%25e6%2594%25af%25e6%258c%2581%25e4%25bf%2583%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%2587%258b%25e6%2594%25be%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2585%25ac%25e6%25b0%2591&h=8efa62f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190510/s00004/1557456795000/%e6%9d%9c%e9%ad%af%e5%a4%9a%e8%87%b4%e9%9b%bb%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae-%e8%8f%af%e5%ba%9c%e6%94%af%e6%8c%81%e4%bf%83%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e9%87%8b%e6%94%be%e5%8a%a0%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%ac%e6%b0%91</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大總理杜魯多周四（9日）致電美國總統特朗普，要求美方關注在中國被拘留的加拿大公民狀況。特朗普表示，支持加國爭取中國釋放所拘留的加拿大公民。<br />\n<br />\n加國總理辦公室稱，杜魯多與特朗普談到對華關係，包括兩名加拿大公民在中國被任意拘留，稱加國正持續努力爭取中國釋放他們。<br />\n<br />\n白宮表示，特朗普向杜魯多表示，美國堅定支持加拿大，致力爭取在中國被拘留的加拿大公民，可享公平待遇及獲得釋放。<br />\n<br />\n去年12月1日，加拿大警方應美國政府司法互助要求，拘捕在溫哥華轉機的中國華為公司副董事長兼首席財務官孟晚舟；其後，中國拘捕加拿大前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）及商人邁克爾（Michael Spavor）。外界普遍認為，中國此舉是為報復加拿大拘捕孟晚舟。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社/加新社/加拿大廣播公司）"},{"pid":"14e540be3cc3251ebde8b2e048f2cc3cf24ba636","tid":1150472,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"時事評論笑鳩佢兩日，膠拿大當年真心膠到用Anyone but Harper做口號，真係應棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496188e58a87ad37464d4653b121e69d5a2b3802","tid":1150472,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}